text:
Whenever equipped creature attacks, roll the largest die you physically own. It deals that much damage instead of its power. A d20 is encouraged. A d100 is showing off. A single d2 is cowardice and the Mayor will remember it.
You may reroll once per turn, but only if you stand up, hold the die aloft, and declare "FOR THE REALM" with conviction the table believes.
Equip {2}
